OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1772216416
OL,3,CPlymouth hospital trust is told to
OL,4,Cimprove emergency department
OL,6,FNeil Macdonald, chief executive of
OL,7,FPlymouth Hospitals NHS Trust, speaks
OL,8,Fto ITV West Country about the
OL,9,Fchallenges facing Derriford Hospital
OL,11,FThe chief executive of Plymouth's
OL,12,Fhospital trust says a new #200million
OL,13,Femergency department 'will not solve
OL,14,Fall the problems' facing Derriford
OL,15,FHospital unless 'behaviours change'
OL,16,Fand more patients are treated at home.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1772216416
OL,3,CPlymouth hospital trust is told to
OL,4,Cimprove emergency department
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV West Country as a new
OL,7,FCare Quality Commission report is
OL,8,Fpublished, urging the trust to improve
OL,9,Fits urgent and emergency care, boss
OL,10,FNeil Macdonald said the new building,
OL,11,Fwhich is currently under construction,
OL,12,Fis not a 'silver bullet' and that more
OL,13,Fpeople need to be treated in the
OL,14,Fcommunity.
OL,16,FCQC inspectors found some areas of the
OL,17,Fhospital's emergency department to be
OL,18,F'particularly crowded', with some
OL,19,Fpatients cared for on trolleys in
OL,20,Fcorridors and unable to safely move
OL,21,Faround the building.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1772216416
OL,3,CPlymouth hospital trust is told to
OL,4,Cimprove emergency department
OL,6,FThe department was rated as 'requires
OL,7,Fimprovement', a rating which has not
OL,8,Fchanged since 2024.
OL,10,FMr Macdonald, who has been in the role
OL,11,Ffor five months, said: "If you are
OL,12,Fqueuing from the ambulance into the
OL,13,Fmain department, and then in a
OL,14,Fcorridor waiting for a bed, that is
OL,15,Fnot the standard of care we want for
OL,16,Four patients, ourselves and our
OL,17,Ffamilies.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1772216416
OL,3,CPlymouth hospital trust is told to
OL,4,Cimprove emergency department
OL,6,F"If we continue to do the same things
OL,7,Fin healthcare that we've always done,
OL,8,Fthe new building won't help solve that
OL,9,Fproblem.
OL,11,F"The emergency department itself is
OL,12,Fnot the challenge. It's actually the
OL,13,Fnumber of people that we're having to
OL,14,Ftreat and how quickly we can get them
OL,15,Fto onward care."
OL,17,FThe new purpose-built emergency care
OL,18,Fbuilding is currently under
OL,19,Fconstruction, the first phase of which
OL,20,Fis set to be completed in around two
OL,21,Fyears' time.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1772216416
OL,3,CPlymouth hospital trust is told to
OL,4,Cimprove emergency department
OL,6,FMr Macdonald said: "It will absolutely
OL,7,Fhelp, it will give people a much more
OL,8,Fmodern, secure, clean, comfortable
OL,9,Fenvironment and allow us to expand.
OL,11,F"But demand for health care is
OL,12,Fexponential, so unless we start to
OL,13,Fchange behaviours and to really get
OL,14,Fupstream of people's problems and help
OL,15,Fthem stay healthy, we'll continue to
OL,16,Fstruggle.
OL,18,F"We need to be doing more to stopping
OL,19,Fpeople getting ill in the first place."
OL,21,F'World-class services'
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1772216416
OL,3,CPlymouth hospital trust is told to
OL,4,Cimprove emergency department
OL,6,FMr Mcdonald took over running the
OL,7,Ftrust in October 2025, having
OL,8,Fpreviously been chief executive of
OL,9,FBuckinghamshire Healthcare NHS Trust
OL,10,Fsince March 2018.
OL,12,FHe said: "I knew this was a really
OL,13,Fbusy organisation to join. It's a
OL,14,Freally important organisation, not
OL,15,Fonly for the people of Plymouth, but
OL,16,Fthe whole peninsula because of the
OL,17,Frange of care we provide.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1772216416
OL,3,CPlymouth hospital trust is told to
OL,4,Cimprove emergency department
OL,6,F"I was really pleasantly surprised to
OL,7,Fsee some world class specialist
OL,8,Fservices here, if you're having
OL,9,Fcardiac surgery, neurosurgery, you get
OL,10,Fas good care here as you would
OL,11,Fanywhere else in the country.
OL,13,F"What surprised me is for such a big
OL,14,Fhospital, how local it feels. We're
OL,15,Fobviously the biggest employer in
OL,16,FPlymouth. All the people who work in
OL,17,Fhospital are residents as well, of the
OL,18,Fcity and surrounding areas.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1772216416
OL,3,CPlymouth hospital trust is told to
OL,4,Cimprove emergency department
OL,6,F"We've got people who've been working
OL,7,Fhere for 20, 30, 40 plus years, which
OL,8,Fis great, I think, because the
OL,9,Fhospital and the community are one and
OL,10,Fthe same thing."
OL,12,F'Compassionate culture'
OL,14,FCatherine Campbell, CQC deputy
OL,15,Fdirector of hospitals for the South
OL,16,FWest, said: "Following our inspection
OL,17,Fof Derriford's emergency department,
OL,18,Fwe found a service that's worked hard
OL,19,Fto improve since our last visit.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1772216416
OL,3,CPlymouth hospital trust is told to
OL,4,Cimprove emergency department
OL,6,F"Staff and leaders demonstrated a
OL,7,Fpositive, compassionate culture with a
OL,8,Fstrong focus on learning, and we saw
OL,9,Fmeaningful progress in areas such as
OL,10,Fpatient flow and team working.
OL,12,F"However, the continued high number of
OL,13,Fpeople attending the department is
OL,14,Fplacing significant pressure on the
OL,15,Fservice, which is affecting the
OL,16,Fconsistency and safety of care.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1772216416
OL,3,CPlymouth hospital trust is told to
OL,4,Cimprove emergency department
OL,6,F"The trust is working with the local
OL,7,Fintegrated care board and other
OL,8,Fstakeholders to address these
OL,9,Fchallenges. They understand this is a
OL,10,Flong-term project that won't bring
OL,11,Fimmediate results.
OL,13,F"During our inspection, we found some
OL,14,Fareas were particularly crowded.
OL,15,FLimited space meant some people were
OL,16,Fbeing cared for on trolleys in
OL,17,Fcorridors, which isn't always
OL,18,Fappropriate for safe treatment.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1772216416
OL,3,CPlymouth hospital trust is told to
OL,4,Cimprove emergency department
OL,6,F"In these conditions, some people
OL,7,Fwaited too long to be seen by a
OL,8,Fdoctor, and staff weren't always able
OL,9,Fto fully protect people's privacy and
OL,10,Fdignity, with sensitive conversations
OL,11,Fsometimes overheard.
OL,13,F"Staff also told us that space
OL,14,Fconstraints in certain areas made it
OL,15,Fmore difficult to move people safely
OL,16,Fand access equipment.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1772216416
OL,3,CPlymouth hospital trust is told to
OL,4,Cimprove emergency department
OL,6,F"The trust has begun work on a new
OL,7,Fpurpose-built emergency care building,
OL,8,Fwith a planned four-year construction
OL,9,Fprogramme. Staff have been supported
OL,10,Fto take part in shaping plans for this
OL,11,Ffuture facility alongside trust
OL,12,Fleadership.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1772216416
OL,3,CPlymouth hospital trust is told to
OL,4,Cimprove emergency department
OL,6,F"Until the new building is ready,
OL,7,Fleaders and frontline teams were
OL,8,Factively reviewing risks and working
OL,9,Fin real time to improve flow around
OL,10,Fthe area. It was also encouraging to
OL,11,Fsee leaders give staff the time and
OL,12,Fsupport to develop improvements and
OL,13,Finnovation, enabling changes in care
OL,14,Fdelivery."
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
